    the libcap-dev Build-Depends and avahi-autoipd.
  * Remove AVAHI_DNSCONFD_START option because we start avahi-dnsconfd by
    default anyway. As /etc/default/avahi-dnsconfd is now empty, remove it on
    upgrades.
