    closes: #438938.
  * Wrap deps, uploaders and build-deps.
  * Add myself to uploaders.
  * Misc whitespace cleanups.
  * Let avahi-daemon depend on bind9-host | host; closes: #433030.
  * Bump up Debhelper compatibility level to 5.

